Package jspecview.exception

Exception Summary
JDXSourceException Thrown when there is an error in the JCAMP-DX Source.
JSpecViewException JSpecViewException is the base class from which all exceptions in JSpecView is inherited.
LDRNotFoundException LDRNotFoundException is thrown when a labled Data Record required to display spectrum is not found.
ScalesIncompatibleException Exception thrown when graphs cannot be overlayed because the scales have different units.
SourceTypeUnsupportedException Exception thrown when the source is not in JCAMP-DX format or the format is unsupported.
SVGException Exception throws when there is a problem creating an SVG from a graph.
TabularDataSetException Exception thrown when there is an error in the Tabular data set that prevents the JDXSpectrum from being displayed.
